{"tid":1851523,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今年仲攪唔攪太平清醮？","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T05:40:47.000Z","uid":190263,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c025217eed75d3e92c658964a46c2fca127465","tid":1851523,"uid":190263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"1. 正評）不了，咩年代仲迷信，聚集人群<br />\n2. 負皮）快點搞， 驅走瘟疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WLM1sa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWLM1sa5.jpg&h=ec2c2972&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1890b188dfd5a1de7ec2588af42a81ca9488b88a","tid":1851523,"uid":190263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"太平清醮活動已傳承了百多年。據長洲島民相傳，清代晚期，長洲曾發生瘟疫，島民死亡枕藉。為求消災，惠潮籍居民延請高僧喃嘸，在北帝廟前設壇拜懺，超渡水陸孤魂，更奉北帝神像綏靖遊行街道，之後，瘟疫果然停止。自此以後，島民每年皆舉辦太平清醮，酬謝北帝神恩，保境平安。百多年來，長洲島居民為禳災祈福，保境安民，一年一度舉辦太平清醮，從未間斷。節慶的豐富傳統內涵，在居民持續多年的參與中，得以傳承發展。長洲太平清醮於2011列入第三批國家級非遺代表性項目名錄。<br />\n<br />\nsource 康文署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/CE/Museum/ICHO/zh_TW/web/icho/representative_list_cheungchau.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2FCE%2FMuseum%2FICHO%2Fzh_TW%2Fweb%2Ficho%2Frepresentative_list_cheungchau.html&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rCKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=2d635b89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/CE/Museum/ICHO/zh_TW/web/icho/representative_list_cheungchau.html</a>"},{"pid":"e5efaf3cbf81bada8d18bc1c4986f10e15619f56","tid":1851523,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAUqTWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAUqTWi.jpg&h=aa0aa640&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}